WEBVTT

00:01:59.434 --> 00:02:03.209
as to why we excuse
so many problematic lyrics;

00:02:03.233 --> 00:02:05.994
it's because we love
how the beats make us feel.

00:02:07.144 --> 00:02:11.202
An example of this is my song
"Top Knot Turn Up."

00:02:14.015 --> 00:02:16.456
(Music: "Top Knot Turn Up")